When it comes to my MTB riding it’s no different. That’s why I’m excited to announce my sponsorship with @industry_nine and ride with confidence on their unyielding set of handmade wheels. 📷 @alex_colorito

#bmx #dmv #atx #motivation

My block button has been on fire lately due to hateful and often racist comments from both strangers and people I know. 

I’m about riding different types of bikes with all different types of people. My page aims to inspire others, spread positivity and encouraging everyone to go after their goals and dreams. 

This noise is not welcome, in my inbox, or in any bike community. If you don’t like it, you can unfollow. 

To all my supporters, I appreciate you. 🙏🏾💯
